593em;">[</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">]</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>中的顶点之间绘制边来将这些参数转换为图，然后将它们视为随机图，等等。然而，对于我在动机部分列出的其他一些问题（例如预测意识形态如何随时间变化），我们需要某种方式来描述争论如何发展。此外，如果我们指定一个随机增长过程，那么该随机增长过程将引发对大小为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的参数的概率测量：我们从空参数开始，并从那里开始增长，直到达到大小<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这个过程非常粗略地反映了争论在实践中如何增长，因此可以合理地预期这样的过程将引发对争论的现实概率度量。另外，我怀疑写下具有某种现实行为的简单论证增长过程比直接写下论证的概率度量更容易。</p><p>让我们将大小为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的自变量定义为函数<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="G_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">G</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; pa